{"data": [{"id": "4742786", "title": "Total Return Breakouts: Palantir, Quantum Computing And Value Investing", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1980358472/image_1980358472.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Quantum Computing Logistics, Quantum Physics, Quantum mechanics\" data-id=\"1980358472\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"960px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1980358472/image_1980358472.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1980358472/image_1980358472.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1980358472/image_1980358472.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1980358472/image_1980358472.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1980358472/image_1980358472.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1980358472/image_1980358472.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1980358472/image_1980358472.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1980358472/image_1980358472.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Just_Super</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>Quantum computing can leverage algorithms to help us outperform in many sectors of our world. Certainly, it is one of the hottest segments in the stock market today. I have spent the last 35 years trading, researching, and constructing algorithms to identify and</p>", "image": "ht