holder\"></div> <p>Why Newly Issued MBS Now?</p> <p>The Federal Reserve Bank (Fed) hiked rates by 525 basis points (bps) over a nearly two-year period, providing attractive yields across all fixed income asset classes. However, Mortgage-Backed Securities (MBS) spreads are trading substantially wider (higher yield) than their historical averages (see Figure 1). Within the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742793-still-great-time-to-consider-mtba", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 12:25:00"}, {"id": "4742782", "title": "NLR: Promising And Still Has An Attractive Price", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157192339/image_157192339.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nuclear power\" data-id=\"157192339\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4992px\" height=\"3328px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157192339/image_157192339.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157192339/image_157192339.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157192339/image_157192339.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157192339/image_157192339.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157192339/image_157192339.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157192339/image_157192339.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157192339/image_157192339.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157192339/image_157192339.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">caracterdesign</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>I recommend buying the VanEck Uranium and Nuclear (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NLR\" title=\"VanEck Uranium and Nuclear ETF\">NLR</a></span>). After years of supply-demand equilibrium and a stable price, uranium prices have surged to record highs and are attracting investor attention.</p> <p>What\u2019s driving this rally is the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157192339/image_157192339.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742782-nlr-promising-and-still-has-an-attractive-price", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 12:15:55"}, {"id": "4742781", "title": "Richmond Mutual Bancorporation: Risk-Return Profile Not Attractive For Long-Term Investors", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Female hand inserting bank card into automatic cash machine (ATM) to access bank account services in the city\" data-id=\"1977075709\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Images By Tang Ming Tung</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Richmond Mutual Bancorporation </strong>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RMBI\" title=\"Richmond Mutual Bancorporation, Inc.\">RMBI</a></span>) is a small regional bank that hasn\u2019t any specific competitive advantage in the banking sector, thus one of its most attractive features of its investment case was its above-average dividend</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742781-richmond-mutual-bancorporation-risk-return-profile-not-attractive-for-long-term-investors", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 12:05:06"}, {"id": "4742787", "title": "U.S. IPO Weekly Recap: ServiceTitan Launches As Small Issuers Slip Through The IPO Window", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"IPO Initial Public Offering 3d concept\" data-id=\"1299608214\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8000px\" height=\"4500px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Olemedia</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Four small IPOs priced this past week, joined by two SPACs.</p> <p>The biggest news came from software provider <strong>ServiceTitan</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TTAN\" title=\"ServiceTitan, Inc.\">TTAN</a>), which kicked off the roadshow for its $480 million offering. It's expected to price in the week ahead.</p> <p>Neuro-inflammation</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742787-us-ipo-servicetitan-launches-small-issuers-slip-through-ipo-window", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 12:00:00"}, {"id": "4742779", "title": "Enterprise Products Partners: Unusual Insider Activities Signal Strong Buy Opportunity", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Buy Text And Red Arrows On White Background\" data-id=\"1145882559\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MicroStockHub/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>EPD stock: co-CEO purchases in focus</span></h2> <p>My last analysis on Enterprise Products Partners (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EPD?hasComeFromMpArticle=false&amp;source=section%253Amain_content%257Cbutton%253Abody_link\" title=\"Enterprise Products Partners L.P. Common Units\">EPD</a>) was published on Nov 1, 2024. In that analysis, I rate the stock as a BUY, as you can see from the screenshot/table below. That</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742779-enterprise-products-unusual-insider-activities-signal-strong-buy-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 11:45:00"}, {"id": "4742778", "title": "Sibanye Stillwater: Still Bullish Going Into 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Sibanye Driefontein Gold 5 Shaft\" data-id=\"878134558\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6200px\" height=\"4134px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">THEGIFT777</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4716545-sibanye-refinancing-likely-strengthens-deep-value-argument\">last covered</a> <strong>Sibanye Stillwater Limited (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SBSW\" title=\"Sibanye Stillwater Limited\">SBSW</a></span>)</strong> <strong>(<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SBYSF\" title=\"Sibanye Stillwater Limited\">OTCPK:SBYSF</a>)</strong> in August, arguing that its stock possessed deep value attributes. Although our rating has yet to strike gold, we believe Sibanye maintains deep value attributes, which many investors haven't spotted.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742778-sibanye-stillwater-still-bullish-going-into-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 11:39:30"}, {"id": "4742776", "title": "Affirm: Wait Now, Buy Later", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"BNPL Buy now pay later online shopping concept.\" data-id=\"1367617255\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"927px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">B4LLS</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>Based on my analysis, Affirm (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AFRM\" title=\"Affirm Holdings, Inc.\">AFRM</a></span>) will continue to expand its market share and make meaningful progress towards profitability. However, my valuation analysis suggests that the company's price is overvalued; there is a possibility that the company may correct</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742776-affirm-wait-now-buy-later", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 11:32:36"}, {"id": "4742774", "title": "A $100,000 Buy-And-Hold Big Dividend Snowball Portfolio", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dollar Seedling - Growth Concept - Plants On Bills In Increase\" data-id=\"1297492947\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"9897px\" height=\"5052px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_12974